Hi, Ive got it working!

Heres some instructions i wrote up for you guys

I tried a few ways but I think this is the one that got it working.

Do apologise if my instructions aren't clear enough

------------------------------------------------------------

Make sure any antivirus software installed on the pc are disabled before installing Autodata


1.Install Autodata (cd1 and cd2)

2.Extract 3.18 Crack.rar into c:\ADCDA2

3.go into c:\ADCDA2\3.18 Crack\Crack1, open both ADBCD.exe and Adkey.exe

4.Copy the Site code from ADBCD.exe and into the Adkey.exe Site code then press OK to 
generate Activation code.Paste this into ADBCD.exe and press OK to unlock

5.now copy all files from Crack1 folder into main folder (c:\ADCDA2) then do the same with 
the files in Crack2 folder

6.now delete the Autodata shortcut from desktop and copy a new shortcut of ADBCD.exe into 
desktop

7.You'l need to adjust the clock everytime you use autodata program. Adjust to around march 
2007 before clicking on the autodata shortcut.Then change back to present date after you've finished

(For those who dont know how to adjust the clock, you need to right click on the time at the 
bottom right corner of the screen and click "Adjust Time/Date)


Hope this information be usefull.
